#: ../new/tiberium/explosive.rst:6
msgid "Tiberium Explosive"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/tiberium/explosive.rst:8
msgid ""
"Tiberium Explosive is the feature that harvester units detonate violently"
" on destruction. It is not to be confused with the similarly named "
"Tiberium Explosion."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/tiberium/explosive.rst:12
msgid ""
"The damage to deliver depends on :tag:`Power` of the contained tiberium "
"bails. This is like it was in :game:`Firestorm`. :game:`Tiberian Sun` "
"also added the harvester unit's strength, which has not been recreated."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/tiberium/explosive.rst:16
msgid ""
":game:`Tiberian Sun` used :tag:`C4Warhead` to deliver the damage, with a "
"hardcoded spread of :value:`1.5`. :game:`Ares` requires the warhead to "
"define :tag:`CellSpread` itself."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/tiberium/explosive.rst:20
msgid ""
"Only positive damage is delivered. In case "
":tag:`TiberiumExplosiveWarhead` is not set or the Harvester Truce feature"
" is enabled, no damage is delivered."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/tiberium/explosive.rst:25
msgid ":tagdef:`[CombatDamage]TiberiumExplosive=boolean`"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/tiberium/explosive.rst:24
msgid ""
"Whether tiberium inside of harvester units explodes using "
":tag:`TiberiumExplosiveWarhead` when destroyed. Defaults to :value:`no`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/tiberium/explosive.rst:29
msgid ":tagdef:`[CombatDamage]TiberiumExplosiveWarhead=warhead`"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/tiberium/explosive.rst:28
msgid ""
"The warhead to deliver the damage of explosive tiberium. Defaults to "
":value:`none`."
msgstr ""

#: ../new/tiberium/explosive.rst:34
msgid ":tagdef:`[CombatDamage]TiberiumExplosiveAnim=animation`"
msgstr ""

#: ../new/tiberium/explosive.rst:32
msgid ""
"Optional animation displayed when Tiberium contained in a unit explodes. "
"Can be used independently of damage delivery; "
":tag:`TiberiumExplosiveWarhead` needs not be set. Defaults to "
":value:`none`."
msgstr ""

